video.title: The Delivery Man
video.synopsis: A cop who has become disheartened by life on the police force resigns and starts a new career as a midwife on a maternity ward.

episodes.synopsis: Searching for personal fulfillment, Matt quits his job as a policeman to become a male midwife, but his first delivery brings a number of problems.
episodes.title: Youth

episodes.synopsis: Matthew's midwifery and diplomatic skills are tested when a man's wife and his mistress both deliver babies at the hospital at the same time.
episodes.title: Truth

episodes.synopsis: Matthew's put in an uncomfortable position when a police inspector asks him to get information from a prisoner who's about to give birth.
episodes.title: Prisoner

episodes.synopsis: When the star of a reality series checks into the hospital, Matthew has trouble keeping her presence a secret from the paparazzi.
episodes.title: Celebrity

episodes.synopsis: When Matthew discovers an abandoned baby, he pleads with his colleagues to keep its presence a secret until Ian can find the mother.
episodes.title: Foundling

episodes.synopsis: When drugs go missing, one of the officers assigned to investigate is Jess, Matthew's ex-girlfriend, whom he believes is carrying his child.
episodes.title: Theft
